#: ../../content/applications/productivity/knowledge/management.rst:91
msgid ""
"To establish this hierarchy, create new articles by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`+` button next to the parent-to-be article, or move existing "
"articles by either dragging and dropping them under the parent-to-be or by "
"clicking the vertical ellipsis button (:guilabel:`⋮`), "
"clicking :guilabel:`Move To` on the toolbox and selecting the article to use "
"as a parent."
